<div class="container bright-section">
  <header class="bright-section__head">
    <h2>Who are the Christadelphians?</h2>
    <p class="bright-lead">
      The name <em>Christadelphian</em> comes from Greek and means &ldquo;brothers and sisters in Christ.&rdquo;
      Christadelphians aim to follow the good news Jesus taught and lived, using the Bible as the authority for faith and practice&mdash;the same hope the apostles spoke of as the hope of Israel.
    </p>
  </header>
</div>

